{"tid":91101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鎖國倒數]工信部:全面禁止使用VPN","createTime":"2017-01-22T15:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T20:49:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb8d0d6e2364ad841ba15752955c2b1a3fe71e5","tid":91101,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:24:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>工信部：不得自行建立或租用虛擬專用網絡VPN等開展跨境經營活動</strong><br />\n<br />\n通知中要求各通信管理局要對本轄區內提供IDC、ISP、CDN業務的企業情況進行摸底調查，杜絕非法經營行為；未經電信主管部門批准，<span style=\"color: red;\">不得自行建立或租用專線（含虛擬專用網絡VPN）</span>等其他信道開展跨境經營活動。<br />\n<br />\n「通知」全文見長圖。 &amp;#8203;&amp;#8203;&amp;#8203;&amp;#8203; <br />\n<img src=\"http://wx1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/9d0d09abgy1fbzi2xvytnj20l732bad7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F9d0d09abgy1fbzi2xvytnj20l732bad7.jpg&h=6ca399e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n工信部link:<a href=\"http://www.miit.gov.cn/n1146295/n1652858/n1652930/n3757020/c5471946/content.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.miit.gov.cn%2Fn1146295%2Fn1652858%2Fn1652930%2Fn3757020%2Fc5471946%2Fcontent.html&d=PX8VkCRn1%2FIEdeDkLZTwqJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=cc744bf6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.miit.gov.cn/n1146295/n1652858/n1652930/n3757020/c5471946/content.html</a>"},{"pid":"1527776b87149584ece378fcfafb6164e16baa0b","tid":91101,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:24:47.000Z","msg":"<strong>二、工作重點</strong><br />\n<br />\n（一）加強資質管理，查處非法經營<br />\n<br />\n1.各通信管理局要對本轄區內提供IDC、ISP、CDN業務的企業情況進行摸底調查，杜絕以下非法經營行為：<br />\n<br />\n（1）<strong>無證經營。</strong>即企業未取得相應的電信業務經營許可證，在當地擅自開展IDC、ISP、CDN等業務。<br />\n<br />\n（2）<strong>超地域範圍經營。</strong>即企業持有相應的電信業務經營許可證，<span style=\"color: red;\">業務覆蓋地域不包括本地區，卻在當地部署IDC機房及服務器，開展ISP接入服務等。</span><br />\n<br />\n（3）超業務範圍經營。即企業持有電信業務經營許可證，但超出許可的業務種類在當地開展IDC、ISP、CDN等業務。<br />\n<br />\n（4）轉租轉讓經營許可證。即持有相應的電信業務經營許可證的企業，以技術合作等名義向無證企業非法經營電信業務提供資質或資源等的違規行為。"},{"pid":"25f99e87b32093399b2579506e35b88870a0dc0a","tid":91101,"uid":17163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:25:06.000Z","msg":"Oh shit~~"},{"pid":"f5adc01788b140765e6e27d3949b68e0d280cff6","tid":91101,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5512701847ad2f04c41fb89d11c675a88ee060","tid":91101,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:26:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa27d44397029c1a04b3145c17975af9d0b47fe0","tid":91101,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a07a7f3f30562e94c6d912d86893dc675101141","tid":91101,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:29:48.000Z","msg":"德政"},{"pid":"eb7a947c30528daa028868e31fe1c6480a753f9f","tid":91101,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:31:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d7c4e1e5523762061c091c5a967eb9b326454af","tid":91101,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:31:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>GJ,記得鎖好d個狗籠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f003e20e311a2002b5c0ecd866fa40c1e0197c","tid":91101,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0333484fd8b86b88da122a861bab4e5e0dfe995","tid":91101,"uid":68325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:33:58.000Z","msg":"電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/n